<i>♪ Let us pause</i>
<i>in life's pleasures ♪</i>

40:47.686 --> 40:49.950
<i>♪ And count it's many tears ♪</i>

40:49.985 --> 40:55.956
<i>♪ While we all sup sorrow</i>
